25,000 pegawai militer...

459
00:40:46,867 --> 00:40:48,369
...seluas 6 juta kaki persegi.

460
00:40:48,535 --> 00:40:49,536
Di mana kamar mandinya?

461
00:40:50,037 --> 00:40:51,755
Dia selalu kencing!

462
00:40:52,539 --> 00:40:53,916
Kau beruntung, Kau akan punya...

463
00:41:21,402 --> 00:41:23,404
DILARANG MEMBAWA MASUK BENDA BESI

464
00:41:55,436 --> 00:41:57,609
Kami dapat siaran di bawah sini.
