498
00:45:34,863 --> 00:45:35,989
Maaf. Kau sudah selesai?

499
00:45:41,954 --> 00:45:43,831
Mereka bilang
kau mengendalikan logam.

500
00:45:44,206 --> 00:45:45,002
"Mereka"?

501
00:45:48,168 --> 00:45:51,388
Dulu Ibuku kenal seseorang
yang bisa melakukan itu.

502
00:45:53,966 --> 00:45:57,186
Maaf, Aku tak suka kekerasan.

503
00:45:59,972 --> 00:46:00,723
Charles?

504
00:46:08,146 --> 00:46:10,069
Aku juga senang melihatmu,
teman lama.

505
00:46:10,232 --> 00:46:11,199
