506
00:46:11,358 --> 00:46:12,826
Bukan karenamu.

507
00:46:14,403 --> 00:46:16,872
Aku tak menyangka
akan melihatmu hari ini.

508
00:46:17,030 --> 00:46:18,373
Percayalah...

509
00:46:18,532 --> 00:46:20,205
...aku takkan di sini
jika tak terpaksa.

510
00:46:20,492 --> 00:46:22,540
Jika kami meloloskanmu,
kita lakukan dengan caraku.

511
00:46:22,703 --> 00:46:23,670
Jangan membunuh.

512
00:46:24,079 --> 00:46:25,080
Tanpa helm.

513
00:46:25,706 --> 00:46:27,708
Aku tak bisa membantahmu
meski aku mau.

514
00:46:27,874 --> 00:46:30,377
Aku takkan masuk
ke kepalamu lagi.

515
00:46:31,712 --> 00:46:33,680
Berjanjilah, Erik.

516
00:46:36,883 --> 00:46:38,055
Jangan bergerak!

517
00:46:38,552 --> 00:46:40,725
Diam di tempat!

518
00:46:42,556 --> 00:46:44,229
Charles. /
Jangan bergerak.

519
00:46:44,391 --> 00:46:46,393
Angkat tangan, Atau kami tembak!

520
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:48,062
Bekukan mereka, Charles. /
Aku tak bisa.

521
00:46:48,270 --> 00:46:49,567
